parameters:
O-our firewood was used by the traveler for the first time!
Wow... Wow!!
Um, how did our firewood turn out...?

Wow... Wow!! It's the otokuisama! It's the repeater! It's my
first fan!
Um, how was our performance...? Did you like it?!

You bastard! What the hell...!!! Damn it, you son of a
bitch...!!!

What is that large amount of bonfires up there? Huh? No, what are
you talking about...? It's obviously the Bonfire Field!

You didn't know...? Geez, you have no common sense... Young
people these days...

D-Don't come any closer...!! This bonfire is mine and mine
alone!! I won't let anyone else use it...!!!
It seems like she's very focused...

Mmm... It feels good. Bonfire should be gently tended and
kneaded. Yes, infuse it with gratitude and warmth firmly...

Can you see it... the newcomer? It's an exquisite rare monster
called Mizukami Bonfire.... I've been doing this job for a long
time, but it's the first time I've laid eyes on it...

What's the meaning of it... you say? Geez, you really don't
understand the elegance...
There is a bonfire on the water...

This is... the fairy village~... High-quality bonfires are the
specialty here~... A secret village~...
It seems like they're having a pointless conversation...
Adult conversations are boring and too long, dechi...

The key is to space the seedlings evenly without wasting any
space when arranging them. Otherwise, the nutrition will become
unbalanced. Ah, of course, a human like you wouldn't make such a
mistake.

This place... it's nice, isn't it? The sunlight is just
perfect... But the rent is quite expensive... Maybe I should pay
and ask for it to be transferred to me... This one square...
It seems like they're getting energized by the bonfire...

The house of the Top who is the most important... Please consult
us when you're in trouble... is written.
N-No...! W-We can't...! It's overwhelmingly... too fast!

Hey, want to try the game I learned from humans? It's said to be
really fun... rubbing our stamens and pistils together...

Actually, in the early stages of Bonfire, we had prepared
different texts for everything... You know, the famous... umm...
like that... Oh.

But during the playtesting, we were told it was annoying so it
ended up becoming just a form of healing with light... Namu,
namu.

The fairy village welcomes other races too, you know. There's no
need for any conflicts. Wait, humans are fighting among
themselves...?

...There's no way there are such idiots! The world is run by much
smarter people! Dechi! Trying to deceive children, how mean of
adults!

I ended up getting lost in a strange place... But I was
unexpectedly welcomed and it became comfortable... Maybe I should
just live here.

Hee, hoo, mee... Yo~... Hmm, the quality and pace are looking
good. With this, our business partners will surely be pleased
with a big smile.
